Acme::DNS::Correct - Fix the DNS System
========================================

Acme::DNS::Correct is a subclass of Net::DNS::Resolver, adding
functionality that returns sanity to the DNS system.  Consult the
Net::DNS manpages for comprehensive documentation on using this module.

See the POD documentation in Correct.pm for more information.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Net::DNS.  The test suite requires
Test::More which is part of the Test::Simple distribution.

